&lt;p&gt;Our franchisees are pivotal to our presence as &lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;the &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;leading pet waste removal company in the US. With over 100 active franchises nationwide, our organization utilizes a service-focused approach to provide a valuable resource for each of our clients.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In your role as a valued franchise owner, the business would thrive under your management as you lead a tech team, maintain routing/schedules &amp;amp; create valuable relationships with the customer base.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For this to happen, we&#39;re looking for passionate candidates who have an interest in owning a growing franchise &amp;amp; operating a business of their own! This doesn&#39;t mean we expect you to know all things about the dirty business of scooping poop. That&#39;s what our team is here for - our support staff works alongside franchisees to ensure that they have the answers needed at any given moment. Join our growing organization as we scoop America&#39;s yards and continue to be #1 at scooping #2!&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Are you a lover of the outdoors? Maybe you&#39;re interested in a straightforward position with minimal management at a competitive rate and amazing benefits. Our organization is serving both coasts in the United States &amp;amp; continues to serve over a 100 cities including Pearland, Sugar Land, and other cities within the South Houston area. Our technicians drive from neighborhood to neighborhood to remove pet waste from yards and other property exteriors. This service has assisted busy families, elderly clients and beyond and continues to be an essential service across the country. Sign-on bonus included* (pending completion of 90 days in the position) Are you ready to be a part of our amazing scooping service team?&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
